          </p>
          <a href="https://resultmarketing.asia" target="_blank" class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-blue-700 transition">
            Get Your Free Marketing Audit →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
